- Tokens must be semantic, not visual (e.g., `bg-card` not `blue-500`).
- Use CSS variables (`--pui-*`) for all tokens.
- No hardcoded colors, spacing, or radii in components.
- Provide dark and light token maps and switch runtime-safe variables.
- Keep typography tokens reusable and platform-agnostic.
- Name tokens for intent (e.g., `surface`, `muted`, `accent`).
- Document token usage and fallbacks.
- Version tokens when changing semantics.